overview: The Irish Comedy Tour is a fast-paced, raucous ride across America with Derek Richards, Mike McCarthy, Derrick Keane and Damon Leibert. The tour opens to a packed Infinity Hall in Norfolk, CT and, along w/behind-the-scenes footage, give us a lighthearted look at life on the road and the high-spirited experience of being Irish in America.
title: The Irish Comedy Tour
